The best thing to do with a clue/entry that just doesn't have that ring, is you dress it up!  So, here we have SPORT UTE (clunk, ugh)...but if you call it "Sport-U-Tiddledy"  you are having a little fun, and you think of "Tiddley-Winks" and get tickled, and maybe snort-chuckle....
